WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.058
♪ Magkahawak ang ating kamay
At walang kamalay-malay ♪

00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:22.513
♪ Na tinuruan mo ang puso ko
Na umibig nang tunay ♪

00:00:26.633 --> 00:00:28.068
Joy, ikaw ba yan?

00:00:28.233 --> 00:00:30.343
Marco? Oo ako to si Joy

00:00:30.467 --> 00:00:31.467
Namiss kita

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:35.184
Ako rin, ang dami kong pinagsisihan
simula nung umalis ka

00:00:36.233 --> 00:00:47.111
♪ La-la-la-la, la-la
La-la, la-la ♪